# ⚙ Installation

## Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/restaurant-management-api.git

cd restaurant-management-api
```

---

## Install Dependencies

```bash
go mod tidy
```

---

## Configure Database

Update your database configuration inside

```
databases/databaseConnection.go
```

---

## Run the Project

```bash
go run main.go
```

The server will start on:

```
http://localhost:8080
```

---

# 🔐 Authentication

Most APIs require a JWT token.

```
Authorization: Bearer <your_token>
```

